org.diylc.appframework.miscutils
Class ConfigurationManager

java.lang.Object
  org.diylc.appframework.miscutils.ConfigurationManager

public class ConfigurationManager
extends java.lang.Object

Utility that reads and writes configuration to an XML file. Each configuration item should have a unique name. To write to the configuration use writeValue(String, Object). Use readXYZ methods where XYZ stands for specific data types.

Author:
Branislav Stojkovic
